n two or three </div><div class="t mdfc x4 he y1a10 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hours of their great test. For it they were unprepared. Jesus </div><div class="t m5d9 x4 he ya57 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">knew better than they the strength of the temptation awaiting </div><div class="t m2a2 x4 he yb30 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them. The Shepherd was to be smitten (Zech. 13:7), and the sheep </div><div class="t mbe2 x4 he yb32 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">scattered. (See margin, John 16:32.) It will be observed that </div><div class="t m480 x4 he y187d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this final stroke to the eleven came suddenly. Another similar </div><div class="t m142a x4 he yc22 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hour of trial awaits the remnant. But a living faith and trust </div><div class="t m894 x4 he y289 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in God and His Word will pass the believer triumphant through </div><div class="t m154 x4 he y687 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this final test into the city Jesus has gone to prepare for His </div><div class="t m600 x4 he y17f6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">saints. </div><div class="t m552 x71 h16 y1931 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON XIII.— Christ&apos;s Last Prayer with His. </div><div class="t mf9 x31 h16 y182e ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Disciples </div><div class="t mcde xb h27 y1873 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SEPTEMBER 24, 1910 </div><div class="t m224 x71 h34 y1b47 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON SCRIPTURE : </div><div class="t m3be x8e he y1748 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">John 17. </div><div class="t ma9d x71 he y1925 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">HELPS: &quot;Desire of Ages,&quot; chapter 73; </div><div class="t m1f2d x9 h16 ye8 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School </div><div class="t m3083 x4 h16 y175b ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Worker. </div><div class="t m22f x71 he y3f5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">PERSONS: Jesus and the eleven. </div><div class="t m607 x71 he y17fb ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">PLACE: On the way to Gethsemane. </div><div class="t m37d x71 he y1842 ff4 fs0 fc0